---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import Link from "./ui/link.astro";
---

<main class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-items-center pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-8">
  <div class="py-6 md:order-1 hidden md:block text-center">
    <img src="/images/hero.png" alt="Hero" srcset="" />
    <a href="https://www.freepik.com/free-psd/bearded-guy-sitting-front-laptop-man-work-computer-freelancer-3d-render-3d-illustration_18054291.htm#query=3d%20avatars%20programmer&position=11&from_view=search&track=ais">Image by pixcel3d</a> on Freepik
  </div>
  <div>
    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight">
      Dev Lab<br />dan Dev Log
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      Situs web ini sengaja dibuat untuk mendokumentasi serta membagikan hal - hal yang saya pelajari atau pun ide - ide yang saya dapatkan di dalam dunia IT, khususnya di bidang pemrograman.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <Link
        href="#"
        href="https://web3templates.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener">
        Get Started
      </Link>
      <Link
        size="lg"
        style="outline"
        rel="noopener"
        href="https://github.com/lobitdev"
        class="flex items-center"
        target="_blank">
        <Icon class="h-4 mr-2" name="simple-icons:github" />
        <span>Lihat Repo GitHub</span>
      </Link>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
